3133.Name: PPL Members, (and Special Guests), Tournament
3133.Details:
1) Women's Tournament - be held on Friday, February 19th
2) Combined PTI less than 50 - to be held on Saturday, February 20th
3) Combined PTI over 50 - to be held on Saturday, February 20th

Tournament Specifics:
1) All draws will be single elimination with a consolation round.
2) Match type to be determined by division directors..
3) All matches will be held at either Bitsy Grant or Cherokee.  To be determined by draw size.
4) Registration is open until February 13th or the first 12 teams.
5) Players may register for one tournament only. 
6) First round matches will start at 9:00am.
3133.RegistrationDetails:
Players must register as a team. 
Registration will be open until 11:50pm on 2/13/21.

3464.Name: 2022 30 Below Smackdown
3464.Details:
Date:  Saturday 1/22
Time:  9:00 - 5:00
Where:  Bitsy Grant Tennis Center
Who:  PTI 30.0 and below
Draw Size:  Limited to the first 10 teams to sign up.  First come first serve.
Cost:  $75 per team.  Includes court fees, Lunch, Drinks, Snacks, Prizes.
